    <div class="faq-a" id="how-long-does-diy-seo-take-to-show-results"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Most websites see measurable ranking improvements within 3 to 6 months of consistent effort. Competitive keywords take longer. Local SEO often shows results faster, sometimes within 4 to 8 weeks. According to <a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/diy-seo/">Ahrefs research</a>, the average page ranking in Google's top 10 is over 2 years old. The key variable is consistency. Publishing 1 article per quarter will not move the needle.</p></div></div>
